Title: Director of Business Intelligence
Description: If you are a hands-on Director of Business Intelligence with experience, please read on!The description below is just a sampling of this role.  If you are interested and you feel you fit let's talk and then we can go into much greater detail!We are a well established company and a leader in our niche industry looking for a Director of Business Intelligence to join our team. Title: Machine Learning Evangelist - Ai
Description: If you are a Machine Learning Evangelist with a passion for Ai, please read on!TItle: Machine Learning EvangelistAlternate titles: Director Market Development, AiLocation: San Mateo, CASalary: $200k - $250k + BonusTransforming the future of healthcare isn’t something we take lightly. It takes teams of the best and the brightest, working together to make an impact. You will be responsible for supporting Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, and Robotic Process Automation (AI/ML/RPA) Market Development for our organization.  You will be reporting to the Chief Data Officer.What You Will Be DoingYou will be a leader for us! You will energetically promote, market, and develop business opportunities and markets for our organization's AI/ML/RPA solutions and capabilities. You will establish and grow relationships across the healthcare and technology industries, networking with other leaders in the space and generating strategic partnership opportunities that pioneer new imaginative possibilities. You will work across the company, business, operations, and development in identifying and prioritizing Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, and Robotic Process Automation capabilities.  This role is a senior role requiring interactions with C-suite, Presidents, GMs, Customers, as well as developers and architects.  You will be representing and speaking on behalf of us at AI/ML/RPA events, leading white papers on AI/ML/RPA and Healthcare, and working with Strategy and the Business on AI/ML/RPA capabilities in our existing and future products.What You Need for this PositionMUST HAVE: - Credibility in the Machine Learning/Ai world- Passion- Creativity, Abstract thinker- Strong business senseMUST WANT TO DO:- Evangelize the vision constantly so all stakeholders are aligned, have context, and understand where we are going. - Represent the customer. Be the champion and voice of customers. Build impactful, personal customer relationships. Bring the customer's voice into the creation process. Own requirements, specifications, and release plans.- Be the subject-matter expert (SME) for the AI/ML/RPA segment including a knowledge of the top ecosystem partners that make up our AI/ML/RPA segment globally.- Own the execution of the strategic plan for each market segment, which includes aligning with partner development managers who manage our technology and consulting partners focused on AI/ML/RPA, maximizing influenced revenue.- Working with partner development managers, build C-level relationships with our top partners and generate interest in new programs focused on AI/ML/RPA- Represent the strategy for AI/ML/RPA to our internal and external stakeholders including the sales teams as well as media coverage and industry events focused on the AI/ML/RPA segment- Help prioritize investment in partners who focus on the AI/ML/RPA market segment to drive incremental results- Execute go-to-market and routes-to-market plans that have clear and measurable ROI models- Work collaboratively internally to drive new solutions to market with our product management, solution architect, and professional service teams- Effectively team with communications, marketing, legal, and support- Identify strategic partners that Change Healthcare may want to recruit into the AI/ML/RPA market segment which could include leading startups, consulting companies, and established technology vendorsWhat's In It for You- Learn from the best!- Work for a well-known company who's product is used by billions across the world- Cutting Edge Technologies- Work on large scalable enterprise applications- Large room for advancement within the company- Amazing Health Benefits- Strong Vacation Policy- Strong 401k - Education ReimbursementSo, if you are a Machine Learning Evangelist with experience, please apply today!Or simply e-mail Madeline@cybercoders.com
